column2: select top # m.mangaid, m.objID, m.objra, m.objdec, m.integr as first_integ, m.rms as first_rms, m.skyrms as first_skyrms into mydb.mangatgssfirst from mydb.mangafirst as m, mydb.TGSS as t   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( t.RA, t.DEC, #) AS n   join dbo.PhotoObjAll as o on o.objID=n.objID
